just have to login to mark ma comment in grace of the legendary Maan Sahab's rendition!  Finally! The maestro has arrived!  and see how much lucky is that lil showoff guy who is sharing stage with the Legend himself, the great Maan Sahab! wah jnaab wah! nazaara hi aagya!  ma ancestors were from Pakistan and still whenever something like that is used which relates to Pakistan, don't know why I feel very nostalgic and emotional!  wish that k kade Punjab nah wandeya jaanda! 
diljit sang well but maan sahab taan fer maan sahab ne!  dhan dhan krati
